  "primary_issue": "The 'deleteBanji' operation lacks any authorization check, allowing any user (including unauthenticated ones) to delete records.",
  "evidence": "In the 'deleteBanji' branch, there is no session or role verification before calling banjiDao.deleteBanji(id). The 'add' branch correctly checks for admin role, but 'deleteBanji' does not.",
